                        <h4>Con Dao</h4>
                        <p>Among top attractions in Vietnam, Con Dao comprises 15 magnificent islands and islets with stunning beaches, glittering coral reefs and scenic bays off the southern coast and isolated from the mainland. Hiking, diving, wildlife-observing and exploring deserted coastal roads and beaches are some recommended activities for tourists visiting this lonely planet.</p>
                        <p>Peak season: May – July.</p>
                        <p>Low season: January – March.</p>
                    </div>
