                        <h4>Da Lat</h4>
                        <p>Regarded as the city of eternal spring, Dalat has a daily average temperature of 15°C minimum to 24°C maximum all year round.</p>
                        <p>This city’s most famous for its farming products including vegetables and flowers, especially the colourful hydrangeas. Conquering the majestic Lang Biang Mountain (or Lam Vien Mountain) is among top things to do in Dalat according to travel review sites.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
